Transit riders bar hop on MUNI|http://blog.sfgate.com|http://blog.sfgate.com/transportation/2015/02/17/transit-riders-bar-hop-on-muni/||2015-02-17|Mission Loc L||By Daniel Hirsch, Joshua Guerci and Laura Wenus

In yet another evening bus adventures, members and supporters of the San Francisco Transit Riders’ Union took to the 14 line last Thursday to migrate from bar to bar in a so-called “PUBlic Transit Crawl” to connect with fellow riders and celebrate Valentine’s Day.

